060,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T15:56:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>郁先release到energy <br />\n唔郁下下食晒好傷結構<br />\n同埋鋼結構會震d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中一二有講過呢樣野<br />\n如果講緊青馬大橋果D更加要<br />\n不過唔知佢地D幅度係點計出來<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Be74HpJpZD4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBe74HpJpZD4&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=a915f661\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Be74HpJpZD4</a></blockquote><br />\n普通deflection<br />\n同埋code of practice有晒要求同計法標準<br />\n點計就教科書有講"},{"pid":"c19086063d3d6507a56386222bbad2163f3f3dc0","tid":198060,"uid":39722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T15:57:22.000Z","msg":"震先正常，唔震你仲驚<br />\n避震嘅一種<br />\n<br />\n利申 專才"},{"pid":"2023154b555cb3629f610705c981606040f7f636","tid":198060,"uid":38066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T15:57:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>郁先release到energy <br />\n唔郁下下食晒好傷結構<br />\n同埋鋼結構會震d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中一二有講過呢樣野<br />\n如果講緊青馬大橋果D更加要<br />\n不過唔知佢地D幅度係點計出來<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Be74HpJpZD4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBe74HpJpZD4&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=a915f661\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Be74HpJpZD4</a></blockquote><br />\n普通deflection<br />\n同埋code of practice有晒要求同計法標準<br />\n點計就教科書有講</blockquote><br />\n但係唔應該震到比用家feel到"},{"pid":"23d03ed8a05b045a08f3051ec2987df8ececbffa","tid":198060,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:01:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>土木撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放心 搖震係無問題<br />\n想知就睇下青馬既起法</blockquote><br />\n原來係咁<br />\n長知識</blockquote><br />\ncivil 有科講dynamic test<br />\n放心啦冇咁易爛<br />\n條橋個span咁長（2個support隔好遠）<br />\n有下墜（deflection）係正常<br />\n只要橋上面（deck）個loading唔好大過cop dead load and imposed load指定既loading <br />\n就唔會塌<br />\n<br />\n利申ive civil hd"},{"pid":"b14602a8db1c0db7bc4be948b5193c4f5bf59799","tid":198060,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:05:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>郁先release到energy <br />\n唔郁下下食晒好傷結構<br />\n同埋鋼結構會震d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中一二有講過呢樣野<br />\n如果講緊青馬大橋果D更加要<br />\n不過唔知佢地D幅度係點計出來<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Be74HpJpZD4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBe74HpJpZD4&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=a915f661\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Be74HpJpZD4</a></blockquote><br />\n普通deflection<br />\n同埋code of practice有晒要求同計法標準<br />\n點計就教科書有講</blockquote><br />\n但係唔應該震到比用家feel到</blockquote><br />\n個wind load大<br />\n行車dynamic都大<br />\n青衣南北橋一樣係咁情況<br />\n你係上面行會感覺到震<br />\n所以每個deck之間會有層膠去吸震<br />\ncon tech 野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n詳細就要俾班main con/路政入黎講解下<br />\n我都唔識"},{"pid":"23e0aeb082cb10645492d1922a7ad4fb9efcf1ac","tid":198060,"uid":92065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:07:24.000Z","msg":"次次行過都feel到<br />\n好似隨時散咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d3db78c292a5e77d3035da8946f9d6b33b463d","tid":198060,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:12:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓都會搖<br />\n唔搖你仲驚啦</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/cqxMmBPOSjQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcqxMmBPOSjQ&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=509ab6e6\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/cqxMmBPOSjQ</a><br />\n之前十號風球都有人影到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實平時樓係一直處於搖動狀態<br />\n風力係一個大約類似倒三角型咁狀態吹向高樓<br />\n樓愈高風愈大<br />\n小學雞常識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過平時既風唔大<br />\n啲樓設計個陣計埋factor of safety（cop wind, bd有晒）<br />\n所以搖動距離得幾mm<br />\n你先睇唔到feel唔到<br />\n<br />\n呢樣野有專門prog做分析<br />\n有興趣可以試下玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f9ee4e1386700cf6f70aa418f1fcf8aea83c17","tid":198060,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:15:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>次次行過都feel到<br />\n好似隨時散咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁可能佢設計個陣考慮既唔係serviceability limited state而係ultimate<br />\n總之唔會咁易散啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假設啲物料冇偷工減料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b5643ea9bce32e767b263b3464480b02694db5","tid":198060,"uid":15271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:25:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實好多橋都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n例如九龍公園</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪行去中港城個條？"}]}